      "content": "thanks! that sounds like a good start. for the \"Dress Codes\" and \"Table Manners\" sections, can u give me some specific examples of what the gold standard is for a high-end professional look and behavior? like, if someone wants to look peak sophisticated on a global stage, what are the \"must-have\" rules they should follow?",
